snippet.title: Torchlight II | Berserker's Dream Trailer
snippet.description:
Pre-order now on Xbox One and PlayStation®4. Nintendo Switch pre-orders coming soon. www.torchlight2.com

Torchlight II will be available on Switch, Xbox One and PlayStation 4 this September 3rd.

The award-winning action RPG is back, and better than ever! Torchlight II brings you back into the quirky, fast-paced world of bloodthirsty monsters, bountiful treasures, and sinister secrets. Once again, the fate of the world is in your hands.

Like: https://www.facebook.com/PlayTorchlight 
Follow: https://twitter.com/PlayTorchlight
